Card.name: The Meathook Massacre
Card.text:
When The Meathook Massacre enters the battlefield, each creature gets -X/-X until end of turn.
Whenever a creature you control dies, each opponent loses 1 life.
Whenever a creature an opponent controls dies, you gain 1 life.

Card.name: Path to Exile
Card.text: Exile target creature. Its controller may search their library for a basic land card, put that card onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle their library.

Card.name: Chandra's Outrage
Card.text: Chandra's Outrage deals 4 damage to target creature and 2 damage to that creature's controller.
